graph LR
    CodeFlare[CodeFlare Operator]

    %% External Dependencies - Required
    CodeFlare -->|embedded v1.38.1| MCAD[MCAD<br/>Multi-Cluster App Dispatcher<br/>Required]
    CodeFlare -->|creates RayClusters| KubeRay[KubeRay Operator<br/>v1.0.0-rc.0<br/>Required]

    %% External Dependencies - Optional
    CodeFlare -.->|embedded v0.3.1<br/>optional| InstaScale[InstaScale<br/>Disabled by default]
    InstaScale -.->|scales when enabled| MachineAPI[OpenShift Machine API<br/>Optional]

    %% Client Library
    SDK[CodeFlare SDK<br/>v0.12.1<br/>Python Client] -->|creates AppWrappers| CodeFlare

    %% Internal ODH Dependencies
    CodeFlare -->|creates Routes/Ingresses| Ingress[OpenShift Routes/Ingress<br/>Internal ODH]

    %% Core Kubernetes Dependencies
    CodeFlare -->|API calls| K8sAPI[Kubernetes API Server<br/>Core]
    CodeFlare -->|metrics| Prometheus[Prometheus<br/>Monitoring]

    %% Integration Points
    Dashboard[ODH Dashboard<br/>Optional UI] -.->|UI for AppWrappers| CodeFlare
    Notebooks[Jupyter Notebooks<br/>RHOAI] -.->|use CodeFlare SDK| SDK

    %% External Services
    MachineAPI -->|provisions VMs| Cloud[Cloud Provider API<br/>AWS/Azure/GCP<br/>External]

